WEBVTT

00:08.764 --> 00:10.315
Pop?

00:10.316 --> 00:12.483
Francis,
I'm in the sunroom.

00:13.931 --> 00:15.381
I'm having a whiskey.

00:15.383 --> 00:16.849
You want one?

00:16.851 --> 00:18.301
We have a guest.

00:18.303 --> 00:20.269
Well, does he want one?

00:20.271 --> 00:22.271
No, she doesn't.

00:22.273 --> 00:25.191
Come, join us.

00:31.065 --> 00:33.566
Hello.

00:33.568 --> 00:35.651
Sister Mary,
Frank Reagan.

00:35.653 --> 00:37.403
Thank you for seeing me.

00:38.373 --> 00:40.573
I didn't know I was.

00:42.410 --> 00:44.794
Oh, I-I'm sorry.

00:46.714 --> 00:48.831
Sister Mary teaches middle
school at St. Dominic's.

00:49.050 --> 00:50.633
Oh.

00:50.635 --> 00:52.418
Well, thanks for your service.

00:52.420 --> 00:55.504
I've got some great memories
of St. Dom's.

00:55.506 --> 00:58.090
Not sure St. Dom's has great
memories of him, though.

00:58.760 --> 01:00.860
What can I do for you, Sister?

01:00.862 --> 01:04.480
I've come to ask you
for an intercession.

01:06.734 --> 01:09.935
Sister, um, whatever
influence I have,

01:09.937 --> 01:11.654
it is purely of this world.

01:11.656 --> 01:14.073
And so is the matter at hand.

01:14.075 --> 01:18.911
Commissioner, I have it from
good sources that St. Dom's

01:18.913 --> 01:20.863
is on a very
short list of schools

01:21.833 --> 01:23.593
the Archdiocese is
considering shutting down.

01:24.431 --> 01:25.918
I'm sorry to hear that.

01:25.920 --> 01:28.537
I've put together a document

01:28.539 --> 01:32.291
that I think makes a good case
for keeping our school open.

01:32.293 --> 01:34.960
Well, again, Sister, this is
way outside my wheelhouse.

01:34.962 --> 01:38.013
But I know you have
a standing lunch

01:38.015 --> 01:39.548
with His Eminence the cardinal

01:40.301 --> 01:41.634
the third Thursday
of each month.

01:43.971 --> 01:45.604
What was I gonna do, hold back?

01:45.973 --> 01:46.889
She's a nun.

01:46.891 --> 01:49.608
If you'd be so kind
as to let me

01:49.610 --> 01:51.170
walk you through our case,
I'm confident

01:52.196 --> 01:53.896
you'd be our very best voice
with His Eminence.

01:53.898 --> 01:56.282
Sister, of course.

01:56.284 --> 01:58.150
I'll listen.

01:58.152 --> 01:59.535
But I can't promise anything.

01:59.537 --> 02:01.153
Oh, no promises expected.

02:01.155 --> 02:02.371
Or accepted.

02:02.373 --> 02:04.757
And, by all means,
get your drink first.

02:05.293 --> 02:06.492
Can I get you something?

02:06.494 --> 02:08.627
Two fingers of bourbon, please.

02:08.628 --> 02:10.413
Over one cube of ice.

02:12.717 --> 02:15.918
I'll have what
she's having.

02:20.174 --> 02:24.176
Police! Anybody! Help!

02:24.178 --> 02:26.395
He's trying
to kill her!

02:26.397 --> 02:28.347
Police!
Police, please!

02:28.349 --> 02:30.015
He's got a knife!

02:30.017 --> 02:31.700
He's trying
to kill her!

02:31.702 --> 02:32.935
Where is he?
Where is he?

02:33.438 --> 02:34.438
On the second floor.

02:36.824 --> 02:38.274
Ma'am, stay here.
Stay here.

02:42.246 --> 02:44.697
Police! Don't move!
You lying bitch!

02:44.699 --> 02:47.032
Drop your weapon!
Get down on the ground!

02:47.102 --> 02:47.950
Drop your weapon!

02:47.952 --> 02:49.201
Eddie, call a bus.

02:49.203 --> 02:50.836
Okay. All right.

02:54.542 --> 02:55.542
Okay.

03:03.851 --> 03:06.852
Okay. Reagan!

03:08.105 --> 03:10.022
Reagan, I don't think
we have time for a bus!

03:10.558 --> 03:11.774
He's going to the roof!

03:11.776 --> 03:14.193
We got to take her to St.
Benjamin's around the corner.

03:14.612 --> 03:16.228
Now! Come on, now!

03:16.230 --> 03:17.897
Come on!

03:19.700 --> 03:21.734
Look at me, look at me,
look at me. Okay.

03:22.370 --> 03:24.119
Help me, help me.

03:24.121 --> 03:25.321
We got you.

03:25.323 --> 03:26.956
We got to get
her to the car.

03:27.008 --> 03:28.190
Wait, wait.

03:29.577 --> 03:31.660
Okay, we got you.

