03:40.087 --> 03:41.847
She's got a pretty deep wound
to her abdomen.

03:41.890 --> 03:43.939
Got it.
We'll take it from here.

03:46.928 --> 03:51.096
We're gonna have to take her
straight to the O.R.

03:55.903 --> 03:58.103
Reagan, behind you!
It's him!

03:58.105 --> 03:59.688
Let's finish this, bitch!

04:05.997 --> 04:08.030
Move. Get her out of the way!

04:08.032 --> 04:09.365
Drop your knife!

04:09.367 --> 04:10.783
Drop your knife!

04:13.838 --> 04:16.704
Reagan.
Get some distance, Reagan.

04:20.428 --> 04:22.011
Get her inside!

04:26.017 --> 04:27.850
Are you okay?
Yeah.

04:27.852 --> 04:29.718
You good?
Yeah.

04:29.720 --> 04:31.387
Stop fighting me.

04:33.808 --> 04:36.191
You all right, Reagan?

04:37.278 --> 04:38.143
Get up!

04:38.145 --> 04:40.195
What do we got here, Reagan?

04:40.197 --> 04:41.897
We got everything
under control here, Mike.

04:42.316 --> 04:42.865
You all right?

04:42.867 --> 04:43.899
You're bleeding.

04:43.901 --> 04:44.950
Nah, it's nothing.

04:44.952 --> 04:46.485
It's not nothing,
you might need stitches.

04:46.538 --> 04:48.378
Yeah, Reagan. You do.
Hey, why don't you let me

04:48.539 --> 04:49.854
take him back
to the house,

04:49.874 --> 04:51.089
while you get
your head looked at?

04:51.158 --> 04:52.374
You prepare an aided card
on the victim.

04:52.376 --> 04:54.493
Nah.
Go ahead.

04:54.495 --> 04:56.745
Hey, hey. What's the problem?

04:56.747 --> 04:58.547
Ask him.

04:59.417 --> 05:02.001
Oh, come on.
We were rookies.

05:02.003 --> 05:04.887
I sort of took credit
for an arrest he made.

05:04.906 --> 05:05.971
Not "sort of."

05:05.973 --> 05:07.339
Just messing with you, come on.

05:07.359 --> 05:08.559
Look, I don't need the collar.

05:08.560 --> 05:11.425
I already made detective.
Oh, yeah.

05:11.429 --> 05:12.194
And you know the difference
between detective third grade

05:12.229 --> 05:13.309
and detective second grade?

05:13.314 --> 05:14.146
What?
Collars. Lots of them.

05:14.148 --> 05:15.814
Any way you can get them.
Seriously?

05:16.651 --> 05:18.100
Reagan, you're
bleeding pretty bad.

05:18.102 --> 05:20.486
Really ought to get it
looked at.

05:20.488 --> 05:21.820
Come on.

05:21.822 --> 05:23.405
Let's go.

05:25.860 --> 05:27.109
He's our collar, Mike.

05:39.373 --> 05:41.340
Hey. Detectives Reagan
and Baez.

05:41.342 --> 05:42.791
You first on
the scene?

05:42.793 --> 05:44.710
Yeah, me and my partner.
What happened?

05:44.713 --> 05:47.211
Well, we're still canvassing,
but we know

05:47.214 --> 05:49.130
two young white guys, driving by...
Uh-huh.

05:49.216 --> 05:50.816
yell some anti-gay stuff
to a guy coming out of the bar.

05:50.851 --> 05:51.884
Then what?

05:51.886 --> 05:53.519
He yelled something back.
They get out of the car

05:53.538 --> 05:54.620
and come at him with a bat.

05:54.772 --> 05:55.554
How bad?

05:55.556 --> 05:57.189
Got his head bashed in
pretty good.

05:57.258 --> 05:58.490
That's where he went down.

06:01.646 --> 06:03.812
Anybody get a good look
at the perps?

06:03.815 --> 06:05.480
Good Samaritan.
Came out of the bar,

06:05.511 --> 06:07.231
got in the middle of it,
threw some punches,

06:07.235 --> 06:09.551
and the punks took off.
Good Samaritan got a name?

06:09.571 --> 06:11.520
Wouldn't give it.
My partner's talking to him.

06:11.906 --> 06:13.706
The guy with the red hoodie.

06:15.459 --> 06:17.076
Red hoodie.

06:17.078 --> 06:18.494
Where the hell's he going?

06:18.913 --> 06:19.578
Hey, yo!

06:19.580 --> 06:21.130
Red hoodie!

06:21.132 --> 06:23.582
Hey, Red Riding Hood, hold on.

06:23.584 --> 06:24.500
Hold on.

06:24.502 --> 06:26.168
I need to ask
you a question.

06:26.470 --> 06:28.137
Fuentes.

06:28.139 --> 06:29.304
Alex?

06:29.306 --> 06:31.557
What are you doing?

06:31.559 --> 06:33.926
You... working under
cover or something?

06:33.928 --> 06:35.427
No.

06:35.429 --> 06:36.645
So, what are you doing,
hanging out

06:36.731 --> 06:38.011
in the West Village
in a gay bar?

06:41.569 --> 06:42.685
Oh.

06:42.687 --> 06:43.986
Uh...

06:43.988 --> 06:46.105
Reagan, please, just
let me keep walking, man.

06:47.324 --> 06:49.605
I-I don't care. Look, did you
get a good look at the guys?

06:50.277 --> 06:52.194
Okay, so you did.

06:52.196 --> 06:54.279
My family finds out, you know?

06:54.281 --> 06:55.614
You know!

06:55.616 --> 06:58.167
I know, but...

06:58.169 --> 07:00.753
Look, you're a witness
to a crime, okay?

07:00.755 --> 07:02.788
You can't just
walk away here.

07:04.508 --> 07:06.341
I'll tell
you what we'll do.

07:06.378 --> 07:08.527
We won't put it
in the squad report,

07:08.546 --> 07:10.295
we'll just put it
in the DA's report.

07:10.381 --> 07:12.547
That way your family
and the squad won't know, okay?

07:12.633 --> 07:13.966
Please, just let me
keep walking.

07:13.968 --> 07:15.934
No. No can do.

